ing St Margaret of Scotland (  d. 1093 ), wife of  King Malcolm Canmore  and daughter of Edmund Ironside of England. It was also the name of the wife of  Henry VI  of England,  Margaret of Anjou  (  1430–82 ), and of  Margaret Tudor  (  1489–1541 ), sister of  Henry VIII , who married James IV of Scotland and ruled as regent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."],"variants":[{"name":"Margareta","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margaretta","meanings":["Formed from Margaret."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Margaret Mecklington was born in 1260. She married John Fallowell Filliol before 1280, in Dorset, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died after 1280."},"et":{"Cir 1260–Aft 1280":"1260–pärast 1280","1258–1280":"1258–1280","1280–1302":"1280–1302","1260–1280":"1260–1280","Cir 1260":"1260","1302":"1302","1258":"1258","after 1280":"pärast 1280","before 1280":"enne 1280","1260":"1260","1280":"1280","Aft 1280":"pärast 1280","Dorset, England":"Dorset, England","Horton, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Horton, Dorset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Cir 1260–Aft 1280":"1260–1280 jälkeen","1258–1280":"1258–1280","1280–1302":"1280–1302","1260–1280":"1260–1280","Cir 1260":"1260","1302":"1302","1258":"1258","after 1280":"1280 jälkeen","before 1280":"ennen vuotta 1280","1260":"1260","1280":"1280","Aft 1280":"1280 jälkeen","Dorset, England":"Dorset, England","Horton, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Horton, Dorset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Cir 1260–Aft 1280":"1260–après 1280","1258–1280":"1258–1280","1280–1302":"1280–1302","1260–1280":"1260–1280","Cir 1260":"1260","1302":"1302","1258":"1258","after 1280":"après 1280","before 1280":"avant 1280","1260":"1260","1280":"1280","Aft 1280":"après 1280","Dorset, England":"Dorset, Angleterre","Horton, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Horton, Dorset, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Margaret Mecklington est née en 12